---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ToiletImage from "../../assets/Protection/Toilet.png";
import ShowerImage from "../../assets/Protection/Shower.png";
import EntryImage from "../../assets/Protection/Entry.png";
---

<section class="xl:container py-20">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-[125px]">
    <div class="px-[120px]">
      <h2 class="text-5xl leading-[56px] font-bold px-[140px]">
        We follow your exact path through the bathroom and add support to it.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="px-[120px] mt-5">
      <p class="px-[140px] text-base leading-[28px]">
        During installation, we ask you (or your family member) to walk us
        through a normal bathroom visit. We watch where you step, turn and
        reach, then plan support around three critical zones.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-20 mx-[240px] px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-row rounded-3xl border gap-8 bg-[#F9F7F7]">
      <Image
        src={ToiletImage}
        alt="Toilet Image"
        class="rounded-s-3xl border"
      />
      <div class="max-w-[525px] mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-[#CC0000] text-xl font-bold">Toilet</h3>
        <p class="text-base font-normal">
          Sit, stand and turn without a wobble
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <p class="text-base font-normal opacity-60">
            We see where you place your hands when sitting and standing, then
            add a fold-down rail beside the seat and floor grip where your feet
            land.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row rounded-3xl border gap-8 bg-[#F9F7F7] mt-8">
      <Image
        src={ShowerImage}
        alt="Toilet Image"
        class="rounded-s-3xl border"
      />
      <div class="max-w-[525px] mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-[#CC0000] text-xl font-bold">Shower / bucket area</h3>
        <p class="text-base font-normal">Wet tiles, anchored movements</p>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <p class="text-base font-normal opacity-60">
            We watch how you step over the lip, turn and use the bucket, then
            place vertical and horizontal bars plus a draining mat in those
            exact spots.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row rounded-3xl border gap-8 bg-[#F9F7F7] mt-8">
      <Image src={EntryImage} alt="Toilet Image" class="rounded-s-3xl border" />
      <div class="max-w-[525px] mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-[#CC0000] text-xl font-bold">Entry & turning</h3>
        <p class="text-base font-normal">The first step in and last step out</p>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <p class="text-base font-normal opacity-60">
            We trace your path between door, toilet and shower, then add a grab
            bar at the main turn and transparent tape along the narrow strip you
            step on most.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer note -->
    <p class="mt-12 text-center text-lg italic">
      Every home is different. We sketch the layout with you before drilling a
      single hole
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
